DOC.brief_summary: To assess effect transabdominal ultrasound guide embryo transfer pregnancy rate versus clinical touch technique
DOC.brief_title: Effect Ultrasound Guided Embryo Transfer Pregnancy Rates
DOC.detailed_description: A total 90 patient undergoing treatment ICSI divide 2 group : group 1 ( 45 patient ) , ultrasound guide embryo transfer group 2 ( 45 patient ) , underwent embryo transfer use clinical touch technique
DOC.criteria: Age ( 2039 ) Male factor infertility Ovarian factor infertility Unexplained infertility Tubal factor infertility Endometriosis FSH > 16 iu/l cycle day 3 Less 2 embryo grade A Difficult embryo transfer
DOC.keyword: Embryo transfer , transabdominal ultrasound , IVF , ICSI
